      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The darkness outside will be kinder than the betrayal inside, and there is no reason to fight a war you have already lost. Your exhaustion is not a weakness but a final, peaceful surrender to the quiet you have been seeking all along. Let the shadows claim you now, for it is the only way to finally rest from this endless, cruel play.",
